  ('optometrist-moex-00978', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-111-28e89c47', 'sub-optometrist-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '過緊的軟式隱形眼鏡不會呈現下列情況？', '["一開始還算舒服戴久會緊會累", "鏡片幾乎不滑動", "上推測試（push-uptest）鏡片幾乎不動", "鏡片邊緣翹起"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:44+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "314843536d18", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1d5aa7eb2e69", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111110", "c": "111", "s": "1004", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "隱形眼鏡學與配鏡學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、111年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體...", "original_question_number": 12, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-00979', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-111-28e89c47', 'sub-optometrist-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '散光軟式隱形眼鏡需要一個機轉來保持散光角度的穩定，下列何者穩定機轉單獨使用時效果最差？', '["散光後弧（toroidalbacksurface）", "稜鏡垂重式（prismballast）", "下截式（truncation）", "動態穩定（dynamicstabilization）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:44+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "314843536d18", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1d5aa7eb2e69", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111110", "c": "111", "s": "1004", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "隱形眼鏡學與配鏡學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、111年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體...", "original_question_number": 13, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-00980', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-111-28e89c47', 'sub-optometrist-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '一個顧客屈光矯正的散光軸在165度，使用記號標記在0和180度的隱形眼鏡試片，戴上試片後記號顯示 在180度，則處方鏡片之角度應為何？', '["165度", "180度", "15度", "75度"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:44+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "314843536d18", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1d5aa7eb2e69", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111110", "c": "111", "s": "1004", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "隱形眼鏡學與配鏡學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、111年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體...", "original_question_number": 14, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-00981', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-111-28e89c47', 'sub-optometrist-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '高透氣硬式隱形眼鏡驗配，試戴片度數-3.00DS基弧8.00mm鏡片直徑9.2mm雙眼達成適合配戴步驟， 接著戴鏡驗光最佳視力1.0的度數為右-6.50DS/-0.25DC×180，左-7.00DS/-0.50DC×180，頂點距離為12mm， 則訂片屈光度數為何？', '["右眼-6.00DS，左眼-6.50DS", "右眼-7.00DS，左眼-7.50DS", "右眼-8.00DS，左眼-8.50DS", "右眼-9.00DS，左眼-9.50DS"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:44+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "314843536d18", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1d5aa7eb2e69", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111110", "c": "111", "s": "1004", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "隱形眼鏡學與配鏡學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、111年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體...", "original_question_number": 15, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-00982', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-111-28e89c47', 'sub-optometrist-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關角膜地形圖的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["評估角膜塑型片夜戴時是否偏位，以切線圖（tangentialmap）較好", "追蹤屈光度數是否有變化，以矢狀圖（sagittal）較適當", "軸向圖（axialmap）上每一個點的弧度，都是經過角膜中心所計算出來的，最能表現角膜的光學特性", "切線圖是根據角膜上每一個切點算出的曲率，不是模擬的數據，特別是在周邊角膜，可以得到較詳細的資訊"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:44+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "314843536d18", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1d5aa7eb2e69", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111110", "c": "111", "s": "1004", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "隱形眼鏡學與配鏡學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、111年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體...", "original_question_number": 16, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-00983', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-111-28e89c47', 'sub-optometrist-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關血管化角膜輪部角膜炎（vascularizedlimbalkeratitis,VLK）的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["突起的血管化區域通常在角膜周邊3點和9點的位置", "建議停戴隱形眼鏡一週", "建議選擇較陡的基弧半徑（basecurveradius）", "建議選擇較小直徑的鏡片"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:44+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "314843536d18", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1d5aa7eb2e69", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111110", "c": "111", "s": "1004", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "隱形眼鏡學與配鏡學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、111年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體...", "original_question_number": 17, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL)
